channel.title: New goals(RSbot)
channel.description:
Well I've been done with rs for over a month now and I've decided to get 99 wc before the acc gets banned. So I'm using RSbot and I've started at level 63. I will post pics and logs. I usually will let the script run every day for about 6-8 hours. Seeing as it gets 5 loads of williows (130 logs) per 15 minutes I think it's possible to reach the goal within the time period of being banned. Currently my acc is still 63 wc so I will just post a pic when I get 70,80,90,95,99 if I do make it that far. I should get done some time around Sunday night reaching level 70-72 if my math is correct.
Script includes good anti randoms for many of the randoms.
Other randoms --------------- Anti ban random mouse
Anti ban chat - "brb full","full load brb","ill brb"
Anti ban player level checks
Anti ban changing
Maybe this script will last me a while.
